## Markdown 流程图

#### 1.使用mermaid制作关系图

**声明图形方向** 

使用 `graph` 参数确定方向

- Code

  ```
  graph TB 					#可选参数 TB  BT  LR  RL
  
  start --> Stop
  ```

- Result

  ![](data:image/jpeg;base64,) 

**设定节点形状和连线** 

  - 1.节点形状: 默认形状为直角框

      - Code

        ```
        graph LR
        A[直角节点]--- B(圆角节点)--- C((圆形节点))--- D>非对称节点]
        E[/输入框/]--- ff[\输出框\]--- G{菱形节点}--- H{{六边形节点}}
        ```

    - Result

        ![](data:image/jpeg;base64,) 

- 1.节点连线

    - Code

        ```
        graph TB
        A1 --text--> B1
        A2 ---|text| B2
        A3 -.text.-> B3
        A4 -.-|text| B4
        A5 ==text=== B5
        A6 ==>|text| B6
        ```

    - Result

        ![](data:image/jpeg;base64,) 

**子流程图** 


  - Code

    ```
        graph TB
        subgraph one
            A1 --> B1
        end
        subgraph two
            A2 === B2
        end
           subgraph three
            A3 -.-> B3
        end
    ```

  - Result

    ```mermaid
        graph TB
        subgraph one
            A1 --> B1
        end
        subgraph two
            A2 === B2
        end
           subgraph three
            A3 -.-> B3
        end
    ```


##### 样式化节点

- Code

    ```
        graph LR
            id1(Start)-->id2(Stop)
            style id1 fill:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px
            style id2 fill:#ccf,stroke:#f66,stroke-dasharray: 5, 5
    ```

- Result

    ![](data:image/jpeg;base64,)  

#### 2.使用flow制作流程图

- Code

  ```
  flow
  st=>start: Start
  op=>operation: Your Operation
  cond=>condition: Yes or No?
  e=>end
  
  st->op->cond
  cond(yes)->e
  cond(no)->op
  ```

- Result

  ```flow
  st=>start: Start
  op=>operation: Your Operation
  cond=>condition: Yes or No?
  e=>end
  
  st->op->cond
  cond(yes)->e
  cond(no)->op
  ```
